!Sample_data_processing = FastQ files aligned to Oryza sativa cv japonica genome v7 nuclear and organelle genomes using GSNAP verion 2011_03_38.
!Sample_data_processing = Count data were generated at gene level using annoations for nuclear, chloroplast and mitochondrial genomes using custom Python script; each gene received a count of +1 if FastQ file aligned in gene region definge in annotation (GFF) file for genome; single read counted multiple times:  if aligned to up to 6 gene regions
!Sample_data_processing = Futher processing for publication was done in R libraries EDAseq and EdgeR
